DEPRECATION WARNING [duplicate-var-flags]: !global should only be written once for each variable.
This will be an error in Dart Sass 2.0.0.

  ╷
1 │ a { $x: 1 !global !global; }
  │                   ^^^^^^^
  ╵
    deprecation-duplicate-var-flags.scss 1:19  root stylesheet

DEPRECATION WARNING [new-global]: As of Dart Sass 2.0.0, !global assignments won't be able to declare new variables.

Recommendation: add `$x: null` at the stylesheet root.

  ╷
1 │ a { $x: 1 !global !global; }
  │     ^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^
  ╵
    deprecation-duplicate-var-flags.scss 1:5  root stylesheet

